To cure Madam Sun's illness,

00:02:37.791 --> 00:02:38.791
Magistrate Sun

00:03:12.000 --> 00:03:14.125
Is this how he atones for his sins?

00:03:18.583 --> 00:03:19.666
What about the monk?

00:03:54.750 --> 00:03:56.041
Living Buddha

00:03:56.708 --> 00:03:58.291
In this life,

00:03:58.500 --> 00:04:00.833
are we destined to suffer endlessly?

00:04:01.625 --> 00:04:04.708
It's hard to find a perfect solution in this world.

00:04:05.125 --> 00:04:06.708
What are you doing? What are you doing?

00:04:06.791 --> 00:04:08.041
What are you all doing?

00:04:10.125 --> 00:04:11.125
Monk

00:04:11.541 --> 00:04:12.833
In this world,

00:04:12.875 --> 00:04:14.958
is there truly no way to have it both ways?

00:04:35.916 --> 00:04:37.083
Monk

00:04:43.916 --> 00:04:45.458
Do you like me?

00:04:48.833 --> 00:04:49.958
Monk

00:04:51.750 --> 00:04:53.250
Do you like me?

00:05:00.833 --> 00:05:02.166
I do.

00:05:48.791 --> 00:05:51.083
People never witness Snow in July

00:05:52.708 --> 00:05:56.500
Joy lingers by ruined walls and a dying hearth

00:06:26.958 --> 00:06:27.958
Lin Xiaoran

00:06:30.666 --> 00:06:31.708
What I owed you

00:06:31.833 --> 00:06:33.333
I had someone make a new one

00:06:38.208 --> 00:06:39.958
Some people can clearly speak

00:06:40.166 --> 00:06:41.791
but always choose to stay silent

00:06:43.083 --> 00:06:46.041
Some should see the wonders of the world

00:06:47.708 --> 00:06:49.625
but would rather lose their sight

00:06:52.250 --> 00:06:53.291
This is not a case of humans

00:06:53.958 --> 00:06:54.958
but a case of ghosts

00:06:55.875 --> 00:06:56.791
Lin Xiaoran

00:06:59.625 --> 00:07:00.625
I lost

00:07:03.875 --> 00:07:06.041
But there's something I still don't understand

00:07:07.166 --> 00:07:10.833
The night Liu Gui secretly brought Liu Qiaoqiao's body home

00:07:11.125 --> 00:07:12.666
The monk never went to the Liu residence

00:07:13.583 --> 00:07:15.958
So who pretended to be Liu Qiaoqiao's ghost

00:07:16.166 --> 00:07:17.708
and scared Madam Liu to death?

00:07:39.041 --> 00:07:42.000
Qiaoqiao, it's all Liu Gui's fault

00:07:42.166 --> 00:07:44.208
I don't know anything

00:07:45.291 --> 00:07:47.750
Just treat me as deaf and blind

00:07:48.000 --> 00:07:50.958
Your matters have nothing to do with me

00:07:52.625 --> 00:07:54.291
You said it's a ghost case

00:07:54.541 --> 00:07:56.875
Do you expect me to ask Madam Liu's ghost?

00:08:10.166 --> 00:08:11.791
Between black and white

00:08:12.083 --> 00:08:13.750
It's hard to tell humans from ghosts

00:08:15.458 --> 00:08:17.875
What a prosperous world this is

00:08:23.000 --> 00:08:26.833
Willows alive, spin the top

00:08:27.666 --> 00:08:31.916
Willows green, fly the kite

00:08:32.666 --> 00:08:37.541
Willows dead, kick the shuttlecock

00:08:38.875 --> 00:08:42.083
Willows alive, spin the top

00:08:42.541 --> 00:08:45.375
Willows green, fly the kite

00:08:45.791 --> 00:08:48.791
Willows dead, kick the shuttlecock

00:08:49.208 --> 00:08:51.958
Sister, why do you sing so beautifully?

00:08:52.000 --> 00:08:53.791
Because I've known how since I was little

00:08:56.750 --> 00:09:01.041
My sister Liu Yanran taught me

00:09:16.708 --> 00:09:17.666
Lin Xiaoran

00:09:19.250 --> 00:09:20.333
According to my investigation

00:09:20.416 --> 00:09:24.000
This book is divided into "The Art of Manipulating People" and "The Art of Ruling a Country"

00:09:24.375 --> 00:09:25.583
And "The Art of Ruling a Country"

00:09:25.666 --> 00:09:28.708
was secretly presented by Magistrate Sun to a powerful figure in the capital

00:09:28.833 --> 00:09:31.500
That's why he was allowed to act arrogantly in Fuan County

00:09:31.916 --> 00:09:33.916
If that's the case, this is a big deal

00:09:34.000 --> 00:09:36.125
Who would dare be interested in ruling the country?

00:09:36.208 --> 00:09:38.708
Don't worry, I'll get to the bottom of this

00:09:40.208 --> 00:09:41.166
Lin Xiaoran

00:09:41.833 --> 00:09:43.541
I’ll give you two choices now

00:09:43.833 --> 00:09:45.625
One, stay and help me investigate

00:09:45.833 --> 00:09:46.916
I choose the second

00:09:48.000 --> 00:09:50.291
Two, be my assistant

00:09:50.541 --> 00:09:52.291
You must not leave my side

00:09:53.208 --> 00:09:54.208
How about it?

00:09:57.041 --> 00:09:59.083
Actually, Li Jingnian

00:09:59.125 --> 00:09:59.708
Hmm

00:09:59.750 --> 00:10:02.375
I came here to say goodbye

00:10:03.500 --> 00:10:05.583
I never agreed to let you leave

00:10:05.666 --> 00:10:07.458
Oh, what about her?

00:10:13.125 --> 00:10:15.750
Lin Xiaoran, how many times has this happened?

00:10:15.875 --> 00:10:16.791
You owe me again

00:10:16.875 --> 00:10:18.125
What’s one more debt?

00:10:18.208 --> 00:10:20.000
Alright, you can pay me back slowly

00:10:20.208 --> 00:10:22.666
This haunted place isn’t safe to stay long

00:10:22.958 --> 00:10:24.000
No matter about this person

00:10:24.125 --> 00:10:26.000
He’s an official from the court

00:10:27.708 --> 00:10:29.583
Deal with him however you want

00:10:29.666 --> 00:10:30.875
Out here in the wilderness

00:10:31.000 --> 00:10:32.666
This kid looks pretty decent

00:10:32.791 --> 00:10:34.291
Sure, he’s yours now